          <text><![CDATA[<p><b>Federal Risk and Authorization Management Program Reform Act of 2018 or the FedRAMP Authorization Act</b></p> <p>This bill amends the E-Government Act of 2002 to establish the FedRAMP Program Management Office within the General Services Administration. The office shall be responsible for the Federal Risk and Authorization Management Program.</p> <p>Additionally, the bill establishes the Joint Authorization Board which shall issue provisional authorizations to cloud service providers to operate within FedRAMP security guidelines.<br /></p>]]></text>
          <updateDate>2018-07-26T04:00:00Z</updateDate>
          <name>Introduced in House</name>
        </item>
